---
import MainLayouts from "../layouts/MainLayouts.astro";
import karenAbout from '../../public/karen-about.jpg';
import graphic from '../../public/graphic.jpg';
import karenGuiding from '../../public/karen-guiding.jpg'
import line from '../../public/line.svg'
---



<MainLayouts title="About" > 
<div class="flex flex-col m-auto items-center justify-center md:max-w-screen-2xl">
    <section class="flex md:text-left text-center flex-col md:flex-row md:gap-16 my-5">
        <img src={karenAbout} alt="Karen" class="md:w-2/5 object-cover m-7 md:rounded-sm rounded-md md:mb-0" />
            <div class="relative">       
                <h1 class="font-poppins md:text-5xl text-2xl font-bold text-[#1D1D1D] leading-11 py-3"> Unlock Success with proven                        
                    <div class="relative inline-block">
                        <svg 
                        class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -z-10 pt-5" 
                        viewBox="0 0 247 15"
                        fill="none" 
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> 
                        <path d="M0 0H123.5H247V15H166.49H0V0Z"         
                        fill="url(#paint0_linear_131_64)"/>
                        <defs>
                            <linearGradient id="paint0_linear_131_64" x1="0" y1="7.5" x2="247" y2="7.5" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                                <stop stop-color="#FFAE4D"/>
                                <stop offset="1" stop-color="#FFDF93"/>
                            </linearGradient>
                            </defs>
                        </svg>                                
                        <span>leadership coaching.</span>
                    </div>
                </h1> 
                
                <div class="flex flex-col">
                    <p class="font-poppins px-4 py-7 text-lg font-medium leading-8 text-[#5E5E5E] "> I am a transformational leadership, business and positive attitude coach, with a successful and proven track record. I have worked with numerous clients from many different backgrounds and business sectors, enabling lasting positive change for my clients.

                    <p class="font-poppins px-4 py-7 text-lg font-medium leading-8 text-[#5E5E5E] ">I hold a Master's Degree in Leadership and Management from Robert Gordon University and a postgraduate certificate in Coaching, from the University of Aberdeen. I am also an accredited coach of the Sue Stone Foundation.</p>
                    
                    <p class="font-poppins px-4 py-7 text-lg font-medium leading-8 text-[#5E5E5E] ">My career has been interesting and varied over the last 25 years. Having first qualifying as a Management Accountant, I very quickly moved into leadership and management where I realised people development was my passion. I have held various Director roles in the corporate world, my last being the CEO of a Scottish based company for 7 years. I live in Aberdeen and work all over Scotland and the UK. I have international clients whom I meet on SKYPE, so distance is not a barrier!</p> 
                </div>       
            </div>  
    </section>
    
    <section class="text-center md:text-left flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 mt-16 ">
             <img src={graphic} class="md:w-1/2 object-cover md:order-1"/>
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="relative inline-block">
                <div class=" relative inline-block ">
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-poppins md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#1D1D1D]"> My Approach 
                    </h1>
                    <svg 
                    class=" absolute bottom-0 w-full -z-10"                    
                    viewBox="0 0 247 15"   
                    fill="none" 
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> 
                        <path d="M0 0H123.5H247V15H166.49H0V0Z"         
                        fill="url(#paint0_linear_131_64)"/>
                        <defs>
                            <linearGradient id="paint0_linear_131_64" x1="0" y1="7.5" x2="247" y2="7.5" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                                <stop stop-color="#FFAE4D"/>
                                <stop offset="1" stop-color="#FFDF93"/>
                            </linearGradient>
                        </defs>
                    </svg>  
                </div> 
                    
                <p class="font-poppins text-xl font-medium py-7 leading-8 text-[#5E5E5E]"> We will start with an informal consultation call. This is for us to get to know each other, for you to share your expectations and desired outcomes, and for me to determine how I can support you proactively. 

                <p class="font-poppins text-xl font-medium py-7 leading-8 text-[#5E5E5E]">You will benefit from my many years of practical experience, my coaching experience, and my dedication to life-long learning. I regularly invest in my own development to ensure my approach remains robust and relevant.</p>

                <p class="font-poppins text-xl font-medium py-7 leading-8 text-[#5E5E5E]">Sessions are held in person in private and comfortable environment, or alternatively via video call. If required, extra support is available by phone and email.</p>
           
            </div>
            
        </div>
   
    </section>
    <section class="flex text-center md:text-left flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 mt-0">
        <img src={karenGuiding} class="md:w-1/2 object-cover mb-5 md:mb-0 m-7 md:rounded-sm rounded-md"/>                
        <div class="flex md:my-14 md:pt-16 flex-col relative md:pb-20">
            <div class=" relative inline-block ">
                <h1 class="font-poppins text-2xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#1D1D1D]"> My Guiding Principles 
                </h1>
                <svg 
                    class=" absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full -z-10"                    
                    viewBox="0 0 247 15"   
                    fill="none" 
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> 
                        <path d="M0 0H123.5H247V15H166.49H0V0Z"         
                        fill="url(#paint0_linear_131_64)"/>
                        <defs>
                            <linearGradient id="paint0_linear_131_64" x1="0" y1="7.5" x2="247" y2="7.5" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                                <stop stop-color="#FFAE4D"/>
                                <stop offset="1" stop-color="#FFDF93"/>
                            </linearGradient>
                        </defs>
                    </svg>  
            </div>     


            <p class="font-poppins text-xl font-medium py-7 leading-8 text-[#5E5E5E]"> I'm here to help you become your best self through positive, non-judgmental guidance, helping you clarify your motivations and goals. As my client, I see you as a talented, capable individual ready to achieve all your life's ambitions.</p>

            <p class="font-poppins text-xl font-medium py-7 leading-8 text-[#5E5E5E]">My coaching approach is comprehensive, acknowledging that we're shaped by our experiences. I use your past to understand your present and future. I provide structured, unbiased coaching, helping you explore your strengths and weaknesses and overcome self-limiting beliefs.</p>

            <p class="font-poppins text-xl font-medium py-7 leading-8 text-[#5E5E5E]">As a team, we respect your personal values, focusing on solutions to your current challenges using your past experiences and values. We'll work collaboratively to create enduring change. Your motivation and engagement can lead us to exceptional results.

            Together, we'll achieve remarkable outcomes.</p>
            <button class="bg-[#1D1D1D] md:w-52 p-4 font-medium md:text-xl rounded-lg text-white md:absolute md:right-0 bottom-0 md: md:mt-15 mx-auto "><a href="/" >Get in touch</a></button>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>    
</MainLayouts>  